OL,5,Cunit
OL,7,FThe family of 22-year-old Lauren
OL,8,FEllis, who died at a mental health
OL,9,Fcentre in in 2017, say they are
OL,10,Frelieved the process is finally over.
OL,12,FIt comes after an open verdict was
OL,13,Freturned at an inquest into her death.
OL,15,FThe Inquest Court found insufficient
OL,16,Fevidence to decide how death occurred
OL,17,Fon Thursday 28 March.
