OL,5,Cunit
OL,7,FLauren was voluntarily admitted to
OL,8,FOberlands Centre on 11 October 2017
OL,9,Ffollowing a series of self-harming
OL,10,Fincidents, but she died by the early
OL,11,Fhours of 12 October.
OL,13,FAfter the inquest, Lauren's mother,
OL,14,FDawn said: "Today's verdict I think
OL,15,Fwas the right one for us you know. I
OL,16,Fdidn't want it to be suicide because
OL,17,Fit wasn't suicide.
