OL,7,F"She was not cared for. She went in
OL,8,Fthere to be safe and looked after and
OL,9,Fit wasn't."JDawn added: "It's good
OL,10,Fthat the legal side has come to a
OL,11,Fclose, but going forward nothing has
OL,12,Freally changed for us, it just carries
OL,13,Fon as normal. She's still not here."
OL,15,FDelivering the verdict, Judge Graeme
OL,16,FMcKerrell said it was hard to
OL,17,Funderstand why the process had taken
OL,18,Fso long.
