OL,7,FHe also said while he was unable to
OL,8,Freach any conclusion, this did not
OL,9,Fsuggest or infer blame on anyone.
OL,11,FA criminal investigation and an
OL,12,Finternal investigation undertaken by
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care into her death
OL,14,Ffound two on duty nurses failed to
OL,15,Fcarry out the necessary checks on
OL,16,FLauren every 15 minutes.
OL,18,FThe investigation also found official
OL,19,Frecords of the checks that should have
OL,20,Fbeen carried out, had been falsified.
